Subject: Unable to get Login screen for China Dev Library link
Description: Users are unable to open below DEV Link in Laptop in India. The DEV link does open in China and in ec2. STG and PROD link does open for users in India. DEV: https://mst-bi.dev.zsservices.cn/MicroStrategyLibrary/ STG: https://mst-bi.staging.zsservices.cn/MicroStrategyLibrary/ PROD: https://mst-bi.zsservices.cn/MicroStrategyLibrary/ While troubleshooting we observed the folowing : •Zscaler enabled with EPP disabled: Link works fine. •EPP enabled with Zscaler disabled. Link works fine. Uploading the logs from user machine while reproducing the issue also uploading the screenshot of Prod Log in window, which is not coming in Dev .
Solution_Comment__c: The customer confirmed that the case can be closed. We did not had an intervention here and the problem was never demonstrated.
